node.text:
Since I haven’t seen the track yet, I hit up the local @chaseelliott9 for some Atlanta Speedway advice. We’re gonna keep it low and consistent. Rights don’t matter! 🏁

@ktmusa @redbull @teamhendrick @supercrosslive @nascar

node.text: The first legend to bring this local hair cut to Unadilla and stop by the @ktmusa pit will get one of my signed @thormxofficial jerseys. Let your trips to the local Barber begin 🔥 ✂️🔥
